&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.csdn.net/qq_28641401/article/details/99428192&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;CentOS 7安装Xfce桌面环境过程_qq_28641401的博客-CSDN博客&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
